      <title>美联储与主要央行立场分歧加剧，美元飙升至 2024 年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/dollar-soars-to-fresh-2024-high-as-fed-diverges-from-major-peers</link>
